Advancing the Frontiers of AI Security

Explore the scientific backbone of Wajibika's intelligent systems.

Our Research Pillars

Wajibika is committed to continuous innovation, with dedicated teams exploring the latest advancements in machine learning, computer vision, and data analytics to refine our crime detection and monitoring capabilities. Our research drives the evolution of public and governmental safety.

Key Research Areas

Predictive Analytics for Crime

Developing sophisticated models to forecast potential crime hotspots and patterns, enabling proactive intervention.

Behavioral Anomaly Detection

Utilizing AI to identify unusual behaviors in real-time video feeds that may indicate illicit activities.

Secure Data Hashing & Encryption

Ensuring the absolute integrity and privacy of all collected data through advanced cryptographic methods.

Human-AI Collaboration Interfaces

Designing intuitive systems that allow human oversight and intervention, blending AI efficiency with ethical human judgment.
